{"tid":487612,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林健鋒：3.11補選「上面」不高興","createTime":"2017-12-03T02:09:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-03T03:10:03.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e2d9bcfe826a9d15b5805bd314a55c5f49a3ae37","tid":487612,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T02:09:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171203/20233037\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171203%2F20233037&d=56lLbbXDiJoF0sy8PSS1jfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=d55a00e5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171203%2F20233037&h=6458e6f2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171203/20233037</a><br />\n<br />\n林健鋒：3.11補選「上面」不高興<br />\n<br />\n要聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171203/large/03la2p04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171203%2Flarge%2F03la2p04.jpg&h=8739ff91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林健鋒指「上面」不滿補選日期。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港府日前正式公佈的立法會補選日期，惹起建制派批評為「對國家政治傳統唔係太熟悉」。政務司司長張建宗昨稱已就補選日子問題「努力過」，但要尊重選管會決定，隨即又有建制派透露，今次事件有令「上面嘅人士」不高興。有民主派反駁建制派斥，「（建制派）與其為自己隨時敗選去賴政府，不如做好選舉工程啦！」<br />\n<br />\n楊岳橋斥怕輸賴政府<br />\n<br />\n港府前日公佈明年3月11日為3個地區及一個功能組別議席補選後，民建聯主席李慧琼即批評，當局安排補選日子，正值北京召開兩會，反映「部份人士對於中國國家政治傳統嘅認識唔係好足夠」。張建宗昨回應稱，明白建制派看法，揚言有「努力過」，「但係最後都要尊重選管會決定」，因為選管會要確保選舉公平、公開、公正。<br />\n<br />\n其後身兼全國政協委員的經民聯林健鋒稱，當局安排的補選日子「有好多人唔高興」，「包括一啲『上面』嘅人士」，但今次事件正好證明，坊間「陰謀論」指北京出手「香港做乜做乜」非事實，「一國兩制都係運作得良好」。盛傳有意派人參與補選的新民黨主席葉劉淑儀稱，不少建制派為人大或政協，兩會期間要返港投票雖不方便，但相信他們能克服，她亦尊重選管會決定。<br />\n<br />\n公民黨黨魁楊岳橋強調，立會補選是香港內部事務，選管會作為獨立機構，當然按公務員提供建議作決定，又批評建制派暗批選管會用意何在，他說「與其為自己隨時敗選去賴政府，不如做好選舉工程啦！」<br />\n<br />\n■記者呂浩然"},{"pid":"09dc4c862123ac09510be0ec8033f0fb8289bddc","tid":487612,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T02:10:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4449d3a805bf8861d913637f2adfa79ca65ae326","tid":487612,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T02:19:49.000Z","msg":"下次選舉會全部人都要撤換！一班狗奴才毫無大局觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c44497eea2e515859471d7dddc8a864b2d78469f","tid":487612,"uid":22858,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T03:10:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>下次選舉會全部人都要撤換！一班狗奴才毫無大局觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>低端五毛優美開始勿吠</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/30/081643_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F30%2F081643_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=3be43dfc&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}